  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK397">
<l>yātāṉum nāṭāmā lūrāmā leṉṉoruvaṉ</l>
<l>cāntuṇaiyuṅ kallāta vāṟu.</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>How is it that any one can remain without learning, even to his death, when (to the learned man) every country is his own (country), and every town his own (town) ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
